#: ../../source/systempreferences.rst:5251
msgid "When TransferWhenCancelAllWaitingHolds is set to \"Don't transfer\", no branch transfer records are created. Koha will not allow the holds to be transferred, because that would orphan the items at the library where the holds were awaiting pickup, without any further instruction to staff as to what items are at the library or where they need to go. When that system preference set to \"Transfer\", branch transfers are created, so the holds may be cancelled."
